WEBVTT

00:03:28.323 --> 00:03:31.011
normally, sex equals baby, eventually.

00:03:31.971 --> 00:03:33.481
But in today's world,

00:03:33.505 --> 00:03:36.384
sex plus pill equals no baby.

00:03:36.408 --> 00:03:37.892
(Laughter)

00:03:37.916 --> 00:03:40.654
And again, we think
that's perfectly normal and natural,

00:03:40.678 --> 00:03:43.528
but that has not been the case
for most of human history.

00:03:43.552 --> 00:03:45.203
And it's not the case for animals.

00:03:45.608 --> 00:03:47.590
What it is does is it gives us control,

00:03:47.614 --> 00:03:50.053
so sex becomes separate from conception.

00:03:50.955 --> 00:03:53.400
And as you're thinking
of the consequences of that,

00:03:53.424 --> 00:03:55.088
then we've been playing with stuff

00:03:55.112 --> 00:03:57.423
that's a little bit more
advanced, like art.

00:03:57.447 --> 00:03:59.525
Not in the sense
of painting and sculpture,

00:03:59.549 --> 00:04:04.226
but in the sense of assisted
reproductive technologies.